text: Tim Driscoll is an American football coach. He is the defensive coordinator at the University of North Carolina at Pembroke. Driscoll served as the head football coach at Finlandia University in Hancock, Michigan from 2015 to 2017. ==References== Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:Finlandia Lions football coaches Category:Fort Lewis Skyhawks football coaches Category:Jamestown Jimmies football coaches Category:Minnesota Crookston Golden Eagles football coaches Category:North Dakota State Bison football coaches Category:Northern Michigan Wildcats football coaches Category:UNC Pembroke Braves football coaches Category:High school football coaches in Utah
